# Accounting Due Documentation

When changing Bank Process frequency, Accounting Due generation, posted dates, billing periods, skip behavior, or automatic status transitions:

- Read `docs/accounting-due-frequency-rules.md` before changing behavior.
- Update that document in the same task whenever behavior or an API contract changes.
- Record examples, date boundaries, period types, single/multi-row behavior, and deferred functionality.
- Keep backend and `Count-frontend` mappings and display behavior aligned.
- Do not wait for the user to request documentation updates.
